    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Ops Approval Workflow\\n\\n1. POST to `/webhook/ai-ops-request` with the request payload.\\n2. n8n calls the FastAPI backend at `$env.AI_OPS_API_BASE_URL` or `http://host.docker.internal:8000`.\\n3. Backend classifies the request with mock or OpenAI LLM mode.\\n4. If `requires_human_review` is true, POST to `/webhook/ai-ops-decision` with `request_id`, `decision`, `reviewer`, and `notes`.\\n\\nNo credentials are stored in this workflow export.",
